fdedbe82-ead9-4148-ba25-781e54619986.title: Elsie
fdedbe82-ead9-4148-ba25-781e54619986.text:
Ooh - that looks like a lovely cup of tea, dearie. Is it for
me?

options.text: No, keep your hands off my tea.

21f3912e-a4ce-4d59-a76e-1cfadb76bb67.title: <player>
21f3912e-a4ce-4d59-a76e-1cfadb76bb67.text: No, keep your hands off my tea.

a25997b2-50fd-4886-a30b-0f1852ab4e31.title: Elsie
a25997b2-50fd-4886-a30b-0f1852ab4e31.text:
Aww. Maybe another time. Anyway, what can old Elsie
do for you?

45318b4b-db50-45f6-b8b5-2a38553785c1.title: Elsie
45318b4b-db50-45f6-b8b5-2a38553785c1.text:
Ahh, there's nothing like a nice cuppa tea. I know what,
I'll tell you a story to thank you for the lovely tea...

efa02221-0842-476f-a577-a40bdd43a365.title: Elsie
efa02221-0842-476f-a577-a40bdd43a365.text:
A long time ago, when I was a little girl, there was a
handsome young man living in Varrock. I saw him here
in the church quite often. Everyone said he was going
to become a priest, and we girls were so sad about that.

6be80c8e-7bc8-4f1d-8e72-80a02ea94988.title: Elsie
6be80c8e-7bc8-4f1d-8e72-80a02ea94988.text:
But young Dissy - that was the young man's nickname
- he was a wild young thing. One night he gathered
some lads together, and after the evening prayer-
meeting they all put on masks and sneaked down to the

417d1631-84b5-42f8-8686-1a1624127126.title: Elsie
417d1631-84b5-42f8-8686-1a1624127126.text:
evil temple in the south of the city, the evil one. The
next day, there was quite a hubbub. The guards told us
that someone had painted 'Saradomin pwns' on the wall
of the Zamorakian temple!

1eb65cf3-124a-4ff0-b785-56a42fd7eaad.title: Elsie
1eb65cf3-124a-4ff0-b785-56a42fd7eaad.text:
Now, we'd always been taught to keep well away from
that dreadful place, but it really did us all good to see
someone wasn't afraid of the scum who live at that end
of town. Old Father Packett was furious, but Dissy just

b283e84e-f42e-47b7-9561-683914247527.title: Elsie
b283e84e-f42e-47b7-9561-683914247527.text:
Dissy left town after that, saying he wanted to see the
world. It was such a shame, he had the most handsome
shoulders...

4467167d-ae51-4713-b2ba-d8b0a7388a09.title: Elsie
4467167d-ae51-4713-b2ba-d8b0a7388a09.text:
A young man came here looking for stories about Dissy
- of course, that's not his proper name, but his friends
called him Dissy - and I told him that one. He said
Dissy had become a really famous man and there was

f4ebe12d-e58b-4cd9-8412-01ef0c8a2468.title: Elsie
f4ebe12d-e58b-4cd9-8412-01ef0c8a2468.text:
going to be a book about him. Well, that's all good, but I
do wish Dissy had just come back to Varrock. I did
miss him so much... well, until I met my Freddie and
we got married, but that's another story.

687c9a3e-d6c8-49bd-bfe5-2aaf96e19142.title: <player>
687c9a3e-d6c8-49bd-bfe5-2aaf96e19142.text: Thank you. I'll leave you to your knitting now.

45f126c6-0d90-414e-9f45-e2ade588649b.title: Elsie
45f126c6-0d90-414e-9f45-e2ade588649b.text: Hello dearie! What can old Elsie do for you?

options.text: Can you tell me a story?
Can you tell me how to get rich?

df8df053-c335-410b-8cd5-431e42530110.title: Elsie
df8df053-c335-410b-8cd5-431e42530110.text:
I'm knitting a new stole for Father Lawrence
downstairs. He could do with something to keep his neck
warm, standing in that draughty old church all day.

options.text: Can you tell me a story?
Can you tell me how to get rich?

4bbc128c-d250-4d6d-b424-8bbb5c9238bc.title: <player>
4bbc128c-d250-4d6d-b424-8bbb5c9238bc.text: Can you tell me a story?

ab44475a-4991-47b1-9f0c-a46be1a6fa5f.title: Elsie
ab44475a-4991-47b1-9f0c-a46be1a6fa5f.text:
Maybe I could tell you a story if you'd fetch me a
nice cup of tea.

e9843e9e-5786-4129-b964-a08d62dd5902.title: <player>
e9843e9e-5786-4129-b964-a08d62dd5902.text: Can you tell me how to get rich?

4abcd6c6-fc6b-4835-a166-e5239eafe058.title: Elsie
4abcd6c6-fc6b-4835-a166-e5239eafe058.text:
Well, dearie, I'm probably not the best person to ask
about money, but I think the best thing would be for
you to get a good trade. If you've got a trade you can
earn your way, that's what my old father told me,

405275d3-e9a4-45ad-bcbe-366e9a37dacb.title: Elsie
405275d3-e9a4-45ad-bcbe-366e9a37dacb.text:
Saradomin rest his soul. I hear people try to get rich
by fighting in the Wilderness north of here or the Duel
Arena in the south, but that's no way for honest folks to
earn a living! So get yourself a good trade, and keep

3100324b-31ba-419f-97d5-0985afeaa4fe.title: Elsie
3100324b-31ba-419f-97d5-0985afeaa4fe.text:
working at it. There's always folks wanting to buy ore
and food around here.
